             sworn. - I live near the prosecutor's at Brentford: I was going past his house, and saw two men at the window; I can only speak to one of them, Ambridge, I am sure he is the person; I did not see them do any thing.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17970426-30-person269">
                  SAMUEL
                   DENNING
               <interp inst="t17970426-30-person269" type="surname" value="DENNING"></interp>
